          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The independent  yields  of fragments of Kr (A = 89 -",
                " 93) and Xe (A = 135 - 142) from photofission of  odd",
                " nuclei   237Np   and   243Am   are   presented.  The",
                " experiments were performed using the  bremsstrahlung",
                " of 25 MeV electrons of the microtron of FLNR JINR. A",
                " technique  was used that includes the transportation",
                " of fragments escaped from the target  with  the  gas",
                " flow  through  a  capillary  and the condensation of",
                " inert gases in a  cryostat  at  the  temperature  of",
                " liquid nitrogen.  Kr and Xe isotopes were identified",
                " by the g-spectra of  their  daughter  products.  The",
                " mass  number distributions of the independent yields",
                " of Kr and  Xe  isotopes  and  of  the  complementary",
                " fragments  (Y and La at photofission of 237Np and Nb",
                " and Pr at the photofission of 243Am) were obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
